<plot>Told from the point of view from Archie (Qualls), a comic book collector, this is the story of a rivalry between two comic book shop owners. One (Logue) does it for the love of comics, while the other shop, run by a husband-and-wife team (Rapaport and Lyonne) are in it strictly for the money. The situation brews to a head when a sneak collector, Conan (Masterson) discovers a large collection of perfectly-preserved classic comics, leading the two shops to vie to acquire them, along with a "villain" (Elwes) who hopes to steal them first.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?111971</url></doc>
